---
spec: openexam/1
title: Classify these RISC-V instructions
points: 3
addons:
  - match
tags:
  - instructions
---

Match each RISC-V instruction to its functional category.

::: match
- `addi` -> arithmetic
- `lw` -> memory
- `beq` -> control flow
- `sw` -> memory
- `slli` -> arithmetic
:::
